---
title: Boneless Honey Garlic Wings with Potato Coins and Carrot Sticks
description: It's Boneless Wing Night at Hello Fresh - pan fried boneless chicken bites tossed in a homemade honey garlic sauce. Quick oven potato coins are the obvious pairing for this pub night dinner. Grab the wet naps because you're going to need them!
